string-array.item:
你可以：


1. 通过帮助、关于界面右上角的反馈按钮来向我发送电子邮件(当你遇到了这个页面没有提及到的问题，或者有新的建议、想法时);


2. 前往酷安网，在完事儿的页面下评论(当你同时还希望听听其他人对你的疑问、建议有什么想法时);


3. 向我捐赠的同时附上你想说的话(当你很喜欢这个应用，一定要向我表达谢意时^_^)。

resources.string:
If you are using some apps that can improve your Android system, or there are such kind of pre-installed apps in your phone, please add EverythingDone to their white-list, otherwise maybe you cannot receive notifications from EverythingDone.

In addition, please grant permissions that EverythingDone requested in permission manager. These permissions are:
(1) Auto boot after phone boots, used to create notifications for Reminder,Habit and Goals;
(2) Read/Write external storage, used to insert file as attachment for things;
(3) Record audio, used to record audio as attachment for things;
(4) Vibrate, help generate better notifications for you to finish things.
EverythingDone promises that it won't use these permissions to do bad things. Thank you.
